==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈɛpɪtæf/}}
* {{audio|en-us-epitaph.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Etymology===
{{etyl|fro}} {{term|epitafe|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|epitaphium||eulogy|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc}} {{term|ἐπιτάφιος||relating to a funeral|tr=epitaphios|sc=polytonic|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ἐπί||over|tr=epi|sc=polytonic|lang=grc}} + {{term|τάφος||tomb|tr=taphos|sc=polytonic|lang=grc}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# An [[inscription]] on a [[gravestone]] in memory of the [[deceased]].
# A [[poem]] or other short text written in memory of a deceased person.

